      <div class="fq-a">Summer season (1 June–31 August): daily 10:00–17:00. Rest of year (1 September–31 May): daily 10:00–16:00. Seal feeding and training sessions run daily at 10:30, 12:30, and 15:30 year-round.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fq">
      <div class="fq-q">Where is Polaria and how do I get there?</div>
      <div class="fq-a">Polaria is at Hjalmar Johansens gate 12, 9007 Tromsø — on the waterfront in central Tromsø, walkable from most city centre hotels in around 10–15 minutes. No dedicated car park; street parking and the Tromsø city car park are nearby.</div>
    </div>
