      <div class="fq-q">Do I need to book Polaria tickets in advance?</div>
      <div class="fq-a">Booking in advance at billett.polaria.no is recommended for weekends and summer visits. The seal feeding sessions do not require separate tickets — they are included in standard admission and run on open schedule.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fq">
      <div class="fq-q">What is included in a Polaria ticket?</div>
      <div class="fq-a">One ticket gives access to all areas: the seal pool and daily feeding sessions (10:30, 12:30, 15:30), all aquarium tanks, all interactive exhibitions, and the panoramic theatre (three films screened on rotation). No separate cinema ticket is needed.</div>
